message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. This product is truly exceptional and I believe it holds immense value for you. Given its quality and features, I am offering it to you for $125. I hope this aligns with your expectations and budget.

Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate the quality of your product, but given my current budget constraints, I am only able to consider offers within the $100 range. I would like to propose a counteroffer of $100 for your product.
